Conti - Copyright Antonio Bartolini 2006 
========================================


Install instructions:
--------------------

1) Create a new database for the application in mySQL 
   and put in the new structure:

# mysqladmin -u USERNAME -p create Conti
# mysql -u USERNAME -p Conti < db.mysql


2) Edit the file: libs/config.inc.php

3) goto: http://yourcontisite/libs/adduser.php

and add users... 

4) goto: http://yourcontisite/

ENJOY! ^_^



